Package: litellmR
Title: Simple Interface to LiteLLM AI Language Models
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("SA", "van der Wulp", , "vdwulp@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a lightweight interface for interacting with LiteLLM AI language models from R. The package offers simple helper functions for sending prompts, handling responses, and integrating LLM calls into data analysis workflows.
